s/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8301eb5a2ae74e0e60e4fde8a9aeabf463ce6f96","tid":809851,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96600928725d0391252de13ed9641c9216641bfe","tid":809851,"uid":13084,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:48:30.000Z","msg":"抵打"},{"pid":"9d8c2c31573953be20060b22edd59017d52a96dc","tid":809851,"uid":59920,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:48:46.000Z","msg":"大6毒撚用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登毒撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a853d9a3882c8fab623290814b37539631d25a6d","tid":809851,"uid":13084,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:48:46.000Z","msg":"唔岩就要打"},{"pid":"55baecce24e2dccf39e215161d498234ca70839f","tid":809851,"uid":49197,"like":28,"dislike":12,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:49:06.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀，去強姦。人生沒有那麼多時間給你演內心戲。愛她就去搞她，喜歡就去強姦。表白有什麼用還是會被拒絕。追不到就下藥，翻臉就發裸照。大不了蹲監獄，你連監獄都不敢蹲還好意思說愛她。出來之後找到她繼續強姦，強姦到讓她開始懷疑自己的人生，讓她覺得她人生的意義就是被你強姦。"},{"pid":"a9a81f9a563feb8e290490809b42b470069b03d3","tid":809851,"uid":1067,"like":57,"dislike":4,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/214908_7a284f2e38df3096d5a4afe5f652d630.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F214908_7a284f2e38df3096d5a4afe5f652d630.gif&h=04368a58&s={S