bJY0WgbVGfko1TIkX5h%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=96c16815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/113812_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif[img]</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5c0a4d028ea8c9ad9ea05a45ece9e01ee82b9f","tid":809851,"uid":144082,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/231314_e3fae9dde636026c4a38ed7a42661b4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F231314_e3fae9dde636026c4a38ed7a42661b4f.png&h=f45cd30e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23885d1884216ce7d08fc1188eee86e7807622d6","tid":809851,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:15:30.000Z","msg":"軒轅劍斬港女啲friend <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862e3cf548f89cd405134702fcf39f0c319452ce","tid":809851,"uid":147923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"修道船重出江湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923c9624c3a4fc4546d4b1b27a9b5aa5b424d214","tid":809851,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"收唔收徒弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c472913d6e644fd6cb15a56aa7444aaaeb36a7e","tid":809851,"uid":74918,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"20歲<br />\n年輕時打過不少零工<br />\n學咗5年泰拳<br />\n咁即係幾歲比人睇唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0090ac7a74278293bf7067f002ee7b9530271e83","tid":809851,"uid":74277,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"話說啱先我在月台閘門前遇到件MK妹 一見到佢就覺得佢好索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後就跟住佢尾上車<br />\n<br />\n上一班車仲好多人好逼 但係呢班車就好空曠 真係嬲 無得同MK妹痴到實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上左車之後我一直企佢隔離 條女不停咁fing下fing下 有幾次頭髮仲撥落我度 我大力咁索 聞到好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但始終觸摸唔到肉體 聞聞下我下體開始有反應 好想佢做我女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMK妹搭左兩個站就落左車 我跟住佢尾 一直行到一條唔知明既巷仔 條女全程係度禁手機 隔離都無曬人 我行快兩步 由背影直至見到佢既側臉 我握實拳頭 深呼吸口氣 一拳向MK妹既腦袋揮去！💥<br />\n<br />\n條女被我一拳knock out後 就向後倒地 訓左係地下 無曬意識 郁都唔郁 我周圍望一望⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「現場環境安全...」<br />\n<br />\n「小姐小姐 聽唔聽到 小姐小姐」我一路叫 一路用雙手拍MK妹膊頭 可惜佢仲係無反應<br />\n<br />\n「先生 呢度有人暈左 唔該你幫我叫白車同拎部AED機過黎」我對住隔離個郵筒講<br />\n<br />\n我用一隻手按住條女額頭 再用兩隻手指抬高佢下巴 檢查呼吸 一邊大力索MK妹細膩清香既秀髮精華<br />\n<br />\n過左十秒 仍然無反應......直覺話俾我聽 一定要進行C.P.R<br />\n<br />\n我雙手合十 放係MK妹既胸部中間 預備按壓<br />\n<br />\n01 02 03 04 05 06 07 08...<br />\n<br />\n做夠30下 我將條女下巴托起 將個嘴對準...<br />\n<br />\n突然間落好大雨 原來係我啲口水 滴到條女成臉都係 睇黎我實在太口渴...<br />\n<br />\n我按實MK妹既鼻 兩嘴輕輕一觸 連我個心都觸埋電 感覺好暖好窩心 <br />\n<br />\n我將舌頭擺入MK妹口中 不斷探索每一個角落 尋求水份 由牙齒到舌頭再到內壁 再大力吮吸MK妹嘴唇和舌頭 吸到盡頭時彈回原位 唾液之花四濺 發出啪嗒啪嗒猶如浪花既聲音 我再重複一次以上步驟 順便將氧氣送到入去 吸一大口精華 再輸入MK妹的喉嚨中 順帶將我吸收多餘既水份歸還 以免條女缺水 之後用舌頭順時針再逆時針360度旋轉10圈 雙唇貼緊密閉真空式呼吸 內裏既唾液忍受唔到壓力而流出 當我鬆開口連住口水絲時 我先發覺<br />\n<br />\n原來我做多左兩個循環..."},{"pid":"bfe89e025aa120cafa3d0b9e10f205164ab33672","tid":809851,"uid":181156,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"喂大佬呀你打唔係問題<br />\n你唔好同人講練五年拳為左打個女人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4605cb5bbe46e1276474f491d2765a0eb21b40bc","tid":809851,"uid":9594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de83320d879f9596b39f74a862e53c6b566a5c76","tid":809851,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"378ae2c8b35f5b58a205820750ebbcc27f5e5cf6","tid":809851,"uid":185010,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ffcc2edb1b9bd20ff6e848612567448221c86f1","tid":809851,"uid":34410,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"86e6d5e4cdfa6b9faf4b48415ba6a0e819cb3f83","tid":809851,"uid":202278,"like":9,"dislike":16,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:45:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"你條毒撚做乜鳩野自己回自己咁折墮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:02:21.000Z","msg":"尋晚Kelly鬧得我好岩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:42:48.000Z","msg":"燃點香煙喝啖酒 所有不快都溜走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條毒撚嬲到逐個cm負皮"},{"pid":"070560a80e7effbd056a55001b08986a97eb9d60","tid":809851,"uid":110832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:43:15.000Z","msg":"毒撚真係好恐怖"},{"pid":"a2ff23239b8ab353687a08415b8b426d2883b4f3","tid":809851,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime